snippet.title: Johnny Depp Speaks on Amber Heard Ruining Her Career
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Speaks on Amber Heard Ruining Her Career

Amber Heard, a lot of people had no idea who she was until her divorce from Johnny Depp. Her biggest role by far is that of Mera, in Aquaman – the love interest of none other than Aquaman himself.

The mess between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp is still ongoing, but when it first started making headlines Amber had released a phone video making Johnny appear to be a drunken abuser.
